er, on the 14th in Macau, China and on the 29th in Singapore. The girl group also announced a second Berlin show on the 19th of September.</p><p> Tickets to (G)I-DLE&#39;s the San Francisco, New York and Chicago shows are available at <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fgidle-tickets%2Fartist%2F2648873" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ticketmaster</a> and will cost $65 to $275.</p><p> Ticketing and venue details for other dates (G)I-DLE&#39;s &#39;I am FREE-TY&#39; world tour are expected in the coming weeks. Keep an eye on this page for the latest information.</p><h2> <strong>(G)I-DLE&#39;s 2023 &#39;I Am Free-ty&#39; world tour dates are:</strong></h2><p> <strong>JUNE</strong><br /> <strong>17: Seoul, South Korea, Jamsil Arena (FINISHED)<br /> 18: Seoul, South Korea, Jamsil Arena (FINISHED)</strong></p><p> <strong>JULY</strong><br /> <b>01: Taipei, Taiwan, Taipei Music Center <strong>(FINISHED)</strong><br /> 02: Taipei, Taiwan, Taipei Music Center <strong>(FINISHED)</strong><br /> 15: Bangkok, Thailand, Thunder Dome <strong>(FINISHED)</strong><br /> 22: Hong Kong, AsiaWorld–Expo<br /> 23: Hong Kong, AsiaWorld–Expo<br /></b></p><p> <strong>AUGUST</strong><br /> <b>04: San Francisco, California, Bill Graham Civic Auditorium<br /> 06: Los Angeles, California, Microsoft Theater<br /> 09: Dallas, Texas, Texas Trust CU Theatre<br /> 13: New York, New York, The Theatre at MSG<br /> 15: Atlanta, Georgia, Fox Theatre<br /> 17: Chicago, Illinois , Rosemont Theatre</b></p><p> <strong>SEPTEMBER</strong><br /> <strong>09: London, England, OVO Arena Wembly</strong><br /> <strong>11: Amsterdam, Netherlands, AFAS Live</strong><br /> <strong>13: Paris, France, Le Zénith</strong><br /> <strong>16: Brussels, Belgium, Forest National</strong><br /> <strong>18: Berlin, Germany, Verti Music Hall<br /> 19: Berlin, Germany, Verti Music Hall (NEW)<br /></strong> <strong>27: Tokyo, Japan, Tachikawa Stage Garde